vote.title: Authorize a three-year cooperative purchasing service price agreement for litigation and pre-litigation support including legal document reproduction services, electronically stored information and electronic discovery services, and trial and pretrial support services for the City Attorney's Office with Delphi Legal Technologies, Inc. through the interlocal cooperative agreement with Dallas Area Rapid Transit - Estimated amount of $300,000.00 - Financing:  Liability Reserve Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
